headline: Assessing NetApp (NTAP) Valuation After Mixed Share Price Performance And Subscription Growth Narrative
summary: NetApp (NTAP) has been drawing attention after a mixed run in its share price, with a small move over the past week, gains over the past month, but a negative total return over the past year. See our latest analysis for NetApp. That pattern, with a recent 5.19% 1 month share price return but a 1 year total shareholder return of a 15.97% decline, suggests shorter term momentum has picked up while longer term holders are still in the red.
